The Palm Ridge Magistrate's Court in Gauteng heard voice notes and text messages from some of the alleged victims, implicating Benjamin Dingiso in the crimes. Manqoba Mchunu has more. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Shocking details of alleged sexual assault emerged against a pastor accused of sexually grooming dozens of young men. The Palm Ridge Magistrate's Court in Gauteng heard voice notes and text messages from some of the alleged victims, implicating Benjamin Dingiso in the crimes. READ: Crime in SA | Dingiso's case postponed to Wednesday This after a whistleblower and former church member testified. Watch the video above for more details on this story.